sequenceDiagram

    Client1->>Client1:Display client chats

    Client1->>+Client1:Selects chat
    Note left of Client1: Inside selected chat
    
    alt chat 
        loop
            Client1->>+Server: send message
            Server->>-Client2: broadcasts message
        end
    else add client
        Client1->>+Server: request client list
        Server-->>-Client1: send client list

        Client1->>Client1: selects client

        Client1->>+Server: request client addition
        Server->>-Server: adds client to chat 
    else get out of chat
        Client1->>+Server: request chat leave
        Server->>-Server: removes client from chat

    else exit
        Client1->>Client1: goes back
    end

